        "type": "text",
        "content": "operation of SPF/PC."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "General tutorial topics may be selected from the Table of Contents."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Many help panels offer a menu of details or additional topics which"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "may be selected by number.  To choose a topic, enter its number in the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "OPTION field, located near the top of the screen."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "If you are interested in accessing a specific topic by name, the Tutorial"
      },
